These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
City: edinburgh, venice, london
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, van, snowmobile
1. the person driving the van is the person traveling to venice##1
2. the person traveling to london is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person traveling to venice##2
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| City      | venice | london | edinburgh |
| Transport   | van     | helicopter    | snowmobile   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, chess
There 3 different types of food: carrot, lemon, pineapple
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person eating pineapple is between the person eating carrot and the person playing canasta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Game   | canasta    | chess        | mah-jongg |
| Food     | lemon | pineapple | carrot         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, disco, rock
House: craftsman, palace, colonial
1. the craftsman house is on the right of the fan country##1
2. the fan country is between the palace house and the fan rock##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Music-Genre   | disco | country     | rock |
| House        | palace  | colonial | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, kale, pomegranate
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, skateboarding, lacrosse
1. the person eating raspberry is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Food   | kale  | pomegranate     | raspberry |
| Sport           | skateboarding | lacrosse | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, indian, argentine
House: modern, townhouse, craftsman
1. the argentine is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the argentine is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the modern house is between the craftsman house and the townhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Nationality   | indian | argentine     | chinese |
| House     | craftsman    | modern | townhouse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, october, september
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, coffee
1. the person drinking water is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in february##2
2. the person who's birthday is in february is the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Birthday   | february  | october   | september        |
| Beverage         | 7up | water | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, pop
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, davidoff, aristoff
1. the fan pop is on the right of the fan classical##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is between the fan pop and the davidoff-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre          | funk  | classical  | pop |
| Cigar   | davidoff | tiparillo | aristoff     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, baking, hiking
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, aconite, iris
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who growsaconite is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | hiking   | drawing  | baking  |
| Flower   | begonia | aconite | iris |

