.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, canasta
3 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, hedgehog
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the person playing canasta and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Game       | canasta | monopoly | mah-jongg  |
| Pet   | hedgehog    | cat        | ferret |

