.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, superhero, family
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, august, november
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person watching action movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre         | family | superhero | action |
| Birthday   | november     | march    | august |

