.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
City: miami, colone, liverpool
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, colonesy, comedy
1. the person watching comedy movies is between the person traveling to colone and the person watching mystery movies##2
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| City   | colone | miami      | liverpool      |
| Movie-Genre       | colonesy  | comedy | mystery |

