2. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching western movies##2
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | june | january   | may   |
| Movie-Genre         | western | comedy | time-travel |

