.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-14::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, red, brown
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, skydiving, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who likes red##1
2. the person who likes brown is between the person who likes red and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Color   | chestnut | brown | red |
| Hobby     | skydiving    | chess    | rock-climbing |

