The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, balloon-flower, poppy
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who growspoppy##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2   |   3    |
| Color   | fuchsia  | apricot   | black  |
| Flower        | balloon-flower | daisy | poppy |

