.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
House: cottage, gothic-revival, colonial
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, hamster
1. the cottage house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is between the colonial house and the owner of the goldfish##2
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| House      | colonial | gothic-revival   | cottage |
| Pet   | hamster  | ferret | goldfish   |

 